     C                     Z-ADDW1MONT    LCKOMM                  MONTH
     C                     Z-ADDW1DAY     LCKODD                  DAY
     C                     TIME           @@TIME
     C                     Z-ADD@TIMEH    LCKOHH                  HOUR
